Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:01.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Hoping to find another trail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Leading to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:06.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}The heavens are waiting for motion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:08.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Fired up for action
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:09.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:10.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:11.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:12.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:12.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:13.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:18.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:21.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:25.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:28.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:33.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:42.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:47.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:52.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:58.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:05.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
